songs.title: Wait
songs.lyrics:
Okay, I do not know how to start this shit
Honestly I do not know what to say
Look, I can not do more music at least until January
I'll be producing music maybe for a friend
On my birthday I will upload "Insane" to my soundcloud account
I have too many problems, problems with the school
Problems with my family
Problems with my girlfriend
I know, everyone has problems, and that's why I decided to stop doing music for a short time
Until I feel good

I will upload the last two songs that remain of "Loop", maybe I have a collaboration with my friend Leonel

Well, he has problems, he does not feel very well
